        "the hour of the wolf coup"
      ],
      "identity": "During the hour of the wolf after Daenerys flees on Drogon, Ser Barristan Selmy and Skahaz the Shavepate seize King Hizdahr \u2014 Barristan kills the pit fighter Khrazz in single combat and takes Hizdahr prisoner on suspicion of the poisoned locusts and the Harpy killings."
    },
    {
